76561198073914869,Recommended,241560,20007285,"Posted: 27 December, 2015",all,HappyFeet,"The Crew has gone through many beneficial changes from when it was first released.The Crew is an open world arcade racer that emphasizes playing with friends and car customization. The map is an abridge vesion of the United States. Major landmarks and cities appear, but smaller, lesser known places are absent from the game. Players can drive on or off the roads, and can use different car ""specs"" to traverse the land easier. These specs can be visually customized to fit the player. Performance upgrades are also available. Car selection is varied but limited. DLCs are available for more cars. The driving physics are arcade-like compared to simulation-like.Note: it is an 'always online' game.Overall, it's a ""meh"" racing game. 6.5/10Buy on sale."
