o 4 person (include you) in a crew.- Canadian border works!Cons:- Need to farm to get a good perfomance part and money.- AI catchup might be annoying if you can't handle it too well.- Overpriced Cars even though they look cheap.- Too bad you can't save your race in the middle of it. if you tend to lose connection, I suggest don't buy since this game required a full internet connection.- Most story missions contain same kind of objective that might make players bored.I'll add more stuff to this review later.I rate it 7.9/10Cheers!"
