st of cars, roads and empty buildings... Main and side quests gives you nothing but common races or driving from A to B. Of course, if you are a big fan of autos, you will most likely enjoy ridings and tunings, and the game will be enjoyable for you. Nevertheless, it's just another Car Simulator that includes game elements from ""Need for Speed"", ""Driver"", etc. We have seen it pretty much times before. The Crew is totally not the first of it's kind.Conclusion: You might enjoy it only if you are a huge fan of autos. Anyway, The Crew is not the glorious one of all Ubisoft projects.2.5/10."
