76561197999474699,Not Recommended,241560,35068663,Posted: 19 September,all,poisonnuke,"What is positive about the game: it is an extremly large map, extremly detailed and diverse. It makes fun to drive through it alone for houres.but what I really hate about the game are the car physics. The police is MASSIVLY overpowered, they are solid like tanks, accelerate faster than the fastest dragster, can make a U-Turn at 200mph, drive through trees, spot you even inside a tunnel from above and fly over roughes surfaces where even a monster truck has problems.And on the other side, you can play the cops as well, but you aint have any of these powers, so it is nearly impossible to catch anyone, despite having luck that the other guy crashes in a corner, where you can pin him down.another thing that is really nagging: the cars are wonderful detailed and close to reality. But only the full-stock version. But you cant to anything with the full-stocks, you need the ""tuned"" version, but there are only a couple of classes like street, perf and circuit for example. Inside these tuned classes, a Koenigsegg Agera R is slower than a Mini Cooper S. Thats ridiculous. So there is nothing special about the cars after theyre tuned.And if you want to drive all cars, it takes you hundreds, if not thousands of hours of ingame playtime, because you need a ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ of money and then after buying the cars, earn all upgrades for each tuned version.And another thing is really nagging: the game is 100% online... and ubisoft is not able to provide stable servers. Prepare for a couple of offline times per week.If these things are no problem for you, the game can make a lot of fun for a while.I have changed my rating to ""do not recommend"". This is because if increasing problems with stability of game and server. The community is decreasing, most of the time you dont find crew members to drive against police.And after hundreds of crate offenses, the police is really a major paint in the a... every time it is EXACTLY the same. The start immediately behind you, have at least 2 times the grip level then you, can drive at least 2 times faster under every condition (like 300kph with circuit spec on offroad, or in bends), have infinity amount of brake power (but if they stick to your back, your brakes render absolutly useless), the chopper can fly like 500 kph, staying in front of you every time, and its lights are blending every one in the party (which is impossible).But there are a lot of other impossibilites the police can do (like stealing your NoS, which is per real definition not possible).And Ive crashed into uncountable invisible walls, which destroyed my car and getting me busted.Why the hell is it impossible, to disable voice chat. Every option from earlier versions is removed, so you have no choice but to disconnect your mic if you want to spare other player from your personal thoughts.There are a lot more things, making the game unrewarding. I didnt felt any sort of enjoyment in the last days, but only anger. Toooooo many obstacles in the game to have at least some fun."
